1.5 Responsibilities
1.5.1 The employer shall: establish the proper delegation framework to comply with this directive;
ensure that this directive is available at the employee's normal workplace during the employee's working hours;
ensure that the manager with delegated authority, in consultation with the employee and the employee's immediate supervisor: determine whether travel is necessary;
ensure that travel arrangements are consistent with the provisions of this directive; and
ensure that accommodation of needs is provided to the point of undue hardship.

